X_num = df[['battery_power', 'clock_speed', 
       'int_memory', 'mobile_wt', 'px_height',
       'px_width', 'ram']]
X_cat = df.drop(['battery_power', 'clock_speed', 
       'int_memory', 'mobile_wt', 'px_height',
       'px_width', 'ram', 'price_range'], axis=1)
In [51]:
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler, LabelEncoder
In [52]:
le = LabelEncoder()
X_cat['m_dep'] = le.fit_transform(X_cat['m_dep'])
In [53]:
scaler = StandardScaler()
scaler.fit(X_num)
X_scaled = scaler.transform(X_num)
X_scaled = pd.DataFrame(X_scaled, index=X_num.index, columns=X_num.columns)
X = pd.concat([X_scaled, X_cat], axis=1)
y = df['price_range']

FEATURE IMPORTANCES¶

In [65]:
plt.figure(figsize=(18,15))

plt.subplot(2,2,1)
importances_rf = model_rf.feature_importances_
indices_rf = np.argsort(importances_rf)

plt.title('Feature Importances - Random Forest')
plt.barh(X.columns, importances_rf[indices_rf], .25, color='purple')
plt.yticks(X.columns, X.columns[indices_rf])
plt.xlabel('Relative Importances(MDI)')

plt.subplot(2,2,2)
importances_gb = model_gb.feature_importances_
indices_gb = np.argsort(importances_gb)

plt.title('Feature Importances - Gradient Boosting')
plt.barh(X.columns, importances_gb[indices_gb], .25, color='orange')
plt.yticks(X.columns, X.columns[indices_gb])
plt.xlabel('Relative Importances(MDI)')

plt.subplot(2,2,3)
importances_xgb = model_xgb.feature_importances_
indices_xgb = np.argsort(importances_xgb)

plt.title('Feature Importances - XGB')
plt.barh(X.columns, importances_xgb[indices_xgb], .25, color='lightblue')
plt.yticks(X.columns, X.columns[indices_xgb])
plt.xlabel('Relative Importances(MDI)')

plt.subplot(2,2,4)
importances_lgb = model_lgb.feature_importances_
indices_lgb = np.argsort(importances_lgb)

plt.title('Feature Importances - LGBM')
plt.barh(X.columns, importances_lgb[indices_lgb], .25, color='lightgreen')
plt.yticks(X.columns, X.columns[indices_lgb])
plt.xlabel('Relative Importances(# of splits)')

plt.show()
